@Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5151
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Login
# @name login
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "passageiro@email.com",
  "senha": "Senha@123"
}

### Criar reserva (requer viagem_van no banco)
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/reservas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "viagemVanId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "itens": [
    {
      "numeroAssento": 1,
      "nomePassageiro": "João Silva",
      "emailPassageiro": "joao@email.com",
      "telefonePassageiro": "21999999999",
      "cpfPassageiro": "12345678909"
    }
  ]
}

### Gerar pagamento Mercado Pago (retorna initPoint)
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/reservas/{{reservaId}}/pagar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Minhas reservas
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/reservas/minhas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Webhook Mercado Pago (simulação — use id real de pagamento)
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/webhooks/pix?id=PAYMENT_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "payment",
  "data": { "id": "PAYMENT_ID" }
}
